### Login
POST {{uri}}/api/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Origin: {{uri}}

{
    "userid": "admin",
    "password": "admin"
}

### User list
GET {{uri}}/api/admin/user
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### User list - search
GET {{uri}}/api/admin/user?search=a
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Add user
POST {{uri}}/api/admin/user
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
    "userid": "user",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "user",
    "grade": ""
}

